 against artery walls',NULL,NULL,1,10),(174,11,'What does \"fever\" mean?','multiple_choice','[\"Low temperature\",\"High body temperature due to illness\",\"Normal health\",\"A headache\"]','High body temperature due to illness',NULL,NULL,1,11),(175,11,'Choose: The doctor _____ me some antibiotics.','multiple_choice','[\"gave\",\"cooked\",\"drove\",\"sang\"]','gave',NULL,NULL,1,12),(176,11,'\"Chronic\" disease means:','multiple_choice','[\"Short-term\",\"Long-lasting\",\"Mild\",\"Curable\"]','Long-lasting',NULL,NULL,1,13),(177,11,'Fill in: I have a sore _____ and cannot swallow.','fill_blank',NULL,'throat',NULL,NULL,1,14),(178,11,'True or False: \"Calories\" measure the energy in food.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','True',NULL,NULL,1,15),(179,11,'What is \"physical therapy\"?','multiple_choice','[\"Medicine\",\"Treatment using exercises and movement\",\"Surgery\",\"A blood test\"]','Treatment using exercises and movement',NULL,NULL,1,16),(180,11,'\"Immune system\" helps the body fight:','multiple_choice','[\"Hunger\",\"Diseases and infections\",\"Sleep\",\"Stress\"]','Diseases and infections',NULL,NULL,1,17),(181,11,'Choose: You should _____ at least 8 glasses of water daily.','multiple_choice','[\"eat\",\"drink\",\"sleep\",\"run\"]','drink',NULL,NULL,1,18),(182,11,'Fill in: Regular _____ helps you stay healthy.','fill_blank',NULL,'exercise',NULL,NULL,1,19),(183,11,'True or False: \"BMI\" stands for Body Mass Index.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','True',NULL,NULL,1,20),(184,11,'What does \"insomnia\" mean?','multiple_choice','[\"Sleeping too much\",\"Difficulty sleeping\",\"A headache\",\"A stomach problem\"]','Difficulty sleeping',NULL,NULL,1,21),(185,11,'\"Surgeon\" is a doctor who:','multiple_choice','[\"Gives advice\",\"Performs operations\",\"Prescribes glasses\",\"Tests blood\"]','Performs operations',NULL,NULL,1,22),(186,11,'Choose: She went to the _____ for a check-up.','multiple_choice','[\"restaurant\",\"hospital\",\"school\",\"library\"]','hospital',NULL,NULL,1,23),(187,11,'\"Vitamin\" is:','multiple_choice','[\"A disease\",\"A nutrient the body needs\",\"A medicine\",\"A type of exercise\"]','A nutrient the body needs',NULL,NULL,1,24),(188,11,'Fill in: Please take this _____ twice a day after meals.','fill_blank',NULL,'medicine',NULL,NULL,1,25),(189,11,'True or False: \"Anxiety\" is a feeling of worry or fear.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','True',NULL,NULL,1,26),(190,11,'What is \"first aid\"?','multiple_choice','[\"Final treatment\",\"Emergency care given before professional help\",\"A hospital ward\",\"A pharmacy\"]','Emergency care given before professional help',NULL,NULL,1,27),(191,11,'\"Stretching\" before exercise helps prevent:','multiple_choice','[\"Hunger\",\"Injuries\",\"Sleep\",\"Thirst\"]','Injuries',NULL,NULL,1,28),(192,11,'Choose: A balanced _____ includes fruits and vegetables.','multiple_choice','[\"sleep\",\"diet\",\"exercise\",\"hobby\"]','diet',NULL,NULL,1,29),(193,11,'What does \"recovery\" mean?','multiple_choice','[\"Getting sick\",\"The process of getting better after illness\",\"A diagnosis\",\"A symptom\"]','The process of getting better after illness',NULL,NULL,1,30),(194,2,'Listen: \"I wake up at 6 AM every morning.\" What time does the speaker wake up?','multiple_choice','[\"5 AM\",\"6 AM\",\"7 AM\",\"8 AM\"]','6 AM',NULL,NULL,1,1),(195,2,'Listen: \"She takes the bus to work.\" How does she go to work?','multiple_choice','[\"By car\",\"By bus\",\"By train\",\"On foot\"]','By bus',NULL,NULL,1,2),(196,2,'Listen: \"We usually have dinner at 7 PM.\" When do they have dinner?','multiple_choice','[\"6 PM\",\"7 PM\",\"8 PM\",\"9 PM\"]','7 PM',NULL,NULL,1,3),(197,2,'Listen: \"He goes jogging in the park every Saturday.\" When does he go jogging?','multiple_choice','[\"Every day\",\"Every Sunday\",\"Every Saturday\",\"Every Friday\"]','Every Saturday',NULL,NULL,1,4),(198,2,'Listen: \"My mother cooks breakfast for the family.\" Who cooks breakfast?','multiple_choice','[\"Father\",\"Mother\",\"Sister\",\"Brother\"]','Mother',NULL,NULL,1,5),(199,2,'Listen: \"I do my homework after school.\" When does the student do homework?','multiple_choice','[\"Before school\",\"During lunch\",\"After school\",\"At midnight\"]','After school',NULL,NULL,1,6),(200,2,'Listen: \"They watch TV in the evening.\" What do they do in the evening?','multiple_choice','[\"Read books\",\"Watch TV\",\"Play sports\",\"Cook dinner\"]','Watch TV',NULL,NULL,1,7),(201,2,'True or False: \"I never skip breakfast\" means the speaker always eats breakfast.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','True',NULL,NULL,1,8),(202,2,'Listen: \"The meeting starts at 9 AM sharp.\" What time is the meeting?','multiple_choice','[\"8 AM\",\"8:30 AM\",\"9 AM\",\"9:30 AM\"]','9 AM',NULL,NULL,1,9),(203,2,'Listen: \"She brushes her teeth twice a day.\" How often does she brush?','multiple_choice','[\"Once a day\",\"Twice a day\",\"Three times a day\",\"Never\"]','Twice a day',NULL,NULL,1,10),(204,2,'Fill in: \"I _____ to bed at 10 PM.\" (go)','fill_blank',NULL,'go',NULL,NULL,1,11),(205,2,'Listen: \"He walks his dog every morning.\" What pet does he have?','multiple_choice','[\"Cat\",\"Dog\",\"Bird\",\"Fish\"]','Dog',NULL,NULL,1,12),(206,2,'Listen: \"We go grocery shopping on Sundays.\" When do they shop?','multiple_choice','[\"Mondays\",\"Wednesdays\",\"Fridays\",\"Sundays\"]','Sundays',NULL,NULL,1,13),(207,2,'True or False: \"I sometimes work overtime\" means the speaker always works extra hours.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','False',NULL,NULL,1,14),(208,2,'Listen: \"She reads a book before sleeping.\" What does she do before bed?','multiple_choice','[\"Watches TV\",\"Reads a book\",\"Exercises\",\"Cooks\"]','Reads a book',NULL,NULL,1,15),(209,3,'According to the passage, what is the best way to save money on flights?','multiple_choice','[\"Book at the airport\",\"Book in advance online\",\"Ask a travel agent\",\"Fly first class\"]','Book in advance online',NULL,'Planning a trip can be exciting but also stressful. To save money, it is best to book flights in advance online. Many airlines offer early bird discounts if you book at least 3 months ahead. You should also compare prices on different websites. Traveling during the off-season is another great way to save money, as hotels and flights are much cheaper.',1,1),(210,3,'When should you book flights for discounts?','multiple_choice','[\"1 week before\",\"1 month before\",\"At least 3 months before\",\"The day of travel\"]','At least 3 months before',NULL,NULL,1,2),(211,3,'What makes off-season travel cheaper?','multiple_choice','[\"Better weather\",\"Lower demand means lower prices\",\"More flights available\",\"Longer vacations\"]','Lower demand means lower prices',NULL,NULL,1,3),(212,3,'What is the main topic of this passage?','multiple_choice','[\"Cooking tips\",\"Money-saving travel tips\",\"Exercise routines\",\"Study habits\"]','Money-saving travel tips',NULL,NULL,1,4),(213,3,'According to the passage, what happened at the hotel?','multiple_choice','[\"The room was dirty\",\"The staff was very helpful and friendly\",\"The food was bad\",\"There was no hot water\"]','The staff was very helpful and friendly',NULL,'Last summer, my family and I traveled to Da Nang, Vietnam. We stayed at a beautiful hotel near the beach. The staff was very helpful and friendly. Every morning, we went swimming in the sea and ate fresh seafood for lunch. In the afternoon, we visited the Marble Mountains and took many photos. It was the best vacation we ever had.',1,5),(214,3,'Where did the family travel?','multiple_choice','[\"Ha Noi\",\"Ho Chi Minh\",\"Da Nang\",\"Hue\"]','Da Nang',NULL,NULL,1,6),(215,3,'What did they do every morning?','multiple_choice','[\"Visited temples\",\"Went swimming\",\"Went shopping\",\"Stayed in the hotel\"]','Went swimming',NULL,NULL,1,7),(216,3,'What did they eat for lunch?','multiple_choice','[\"Pizza\",\"Fresh seafood\",\"Rice\",\"Noodles\"]','Fresh seafood',NULL,NULL,1,8),(217,3,'True or False: They visited the Marble Mountains in the morning.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','False',NULL,NULL,1,9),(218,3,'According to the passage, why is a passport important?','multiple_choice','[\"To buy souvenirs\",\"It is required to enter another country\",\"To book hotels\",\"To rent a car\"]','It is required to enter another country',NULL,'When traveling abroad, there are several important documents you must prepare. First, you need a valid passport. Some countries also require a visa, which you must apply for before your trip. It is wise to make copies of all your documents and keep them in a separate bag. You should also have travel insurance in case of emergencies such as lost luggage or medical problems.',1,10),(219,3,'What should you do with copies of your documents?','multiple_choice','[\"Throw them away\",\"Keep in the same bag\",\"Keep in a separate bag\",\"Give to a friend\"]','Keep in a separate bag',NULL,NULL,1,11),(220,3,'Why is travel insurance important?','multiple_choice','[\"For discounts\",\"For emergencies like lost luggage or medical problems\",\"For booking flights\",\"For getting visas\"]','For emergencies like lost luggage or medical problems',NULL,NULL,1,12),(221,3,'Fill in: You need a valid _____ to travel abroad.','fill_blank',NULL,'passport',NULL,NULL,1,13),(222,3,'True or False: All countries require a visa for entry.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','False',NULL,NULL,1,14),(223,3,'What is the main advice of the passage?','multiple_choice','[\"Travel light\",\"Prepare documents carefully before traveling\",\"Always fly first class\",\"Never buy insurance\"]','Prepare documents carefully before traveling',NULL,NULL,1,15),(224,6,'What is the main idea of this passage?','multiple_choice','[\"How to exercise\",\"The importance of a balanced diet\",\"How to travel\",\"How to study\"]','The importance of a balanced diet',NULL,'A balanced diet is essential for good health. It should include a variety of foods from all food groups: fruits, vegetables, grains, protein, and dairy. Eating too much processed food can lead to health problems such as obesity, heart disease, and diabetes. Experts recommend eating at least five servings of fruits and vegetables every day. Drinking plenty of water is also important for staying healthy.',1,1),(225,6,'How many servings of fruits and vegetables are recommended?','multiple_choice','[\"Two\",\"Three\",\"Four\",\"At least five\"]','At least five',NULL,NULL,1,2),(226,6,'What problems can processed food cause?','multiple_choice','[\"Better health\",\"Obesity, heart disease, and diabetes\",\"More energy\",\"Better sleep\"]','Obesity, heart disease, and diabetes',NULL,NULL,1,3),(227,6,'True or False: Drinking water is important for health.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','True',NULL,NULL,1,4),(228,6,'Fill in: A balanced _____ includes all food groups.','fill_blank',NULL,'diet',NULL,NULL,1,5),(229,6,'According to the passage, what is pho?','multiple_choice','[\"A dessert\",\"A traditional Vietnamese noodle soup\",\"A type of fruit\",\"A drink\"]','A traditional Vietnamese noodle soup',NULL,'Vietnamese cuisine is known worldwide for its fresh ingredients and unique flavors. Pho, a traditional noodle soup, is one of the most famous dishes. It is made with rice noodles, herbs, and either beef or chicken broth. Another popular dish is banh mi, a Vietnamese sandwich with French influence. Vietnamese food often uses fresh herbs like mint, cilantro, and basil, which give the dishes their distinctive taste.',1,6),(230,6,'What are the main ingredients of pho?','multiple_choice','[\"Wheat noodles and cheese\",\"Rice noodles, herbs, and broth\",\"Bread and butter\",\"Pasta and tomato sauce\"]','Rice noodles, herbs, and broth',NULL,NULL,1,7),(231,6,'What is banh mi?','multiple_choice','[\"A soup\",\"A Vietnamese sandwich\",\"A dessert\",\"A drink\"]','A Vietnamese sandwich',NULL,NULL,1,8),(232,6,'Which herbs are commonly used in Vietnamese food?','multiple_choice','[\"Rosemary and thyme\",\"Mint, cilantro, and basil\",\"Oregano and parsley\",\"Dill and sage\"]','Mint, cilantro, and basil',NULL,NULL,1,9),(233,6,'True or False: Banh mi has French influence.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','True',NULL,NULL,1,10),(234,6,'According to the passage, what has become trendy recently?','multiple_choice','[\"Fast food\",\"Farm-to-table dining\",\"Frozen food\",\"Canned food\"]','Farm-to-table dining',NULL,'The farm-to-table movement has become very popular in recent years. This concept means that restaurants buy ingredients directly from local farms. The food is fresher and more nutritious because it does not travel long distances. This also helps support local farmers and reduces the environmental impact of food transportation. Many people prefer farm-to-table restaurants because they know exactly where their food comes from.',1,11),(235,6,'Why is farm-to-table food fresher?','multiple_choice','[\"It is frozen\",\"It does not travel long distances\",\"It is imported\",\"It is processed\"]','It does not travel long distances',NULL,NULL,1,12),(236,6,'How does farm-to-table help the environment?','multiple_choice','[\"Uses more packaging\",\"Reduces food transportation impact\",\"Uses more electricity\",\"Produces more waste\"]','Reduces food transportation impact',NULL,NULL,1,13),(237,6,'Fill in: Farm-to-table restaurants buy from local _____.','fill_blank',NULL,'farms',NULL,NULL,1,14),(238,6,'What is the main benefit for consumers?','multiple_choice','[\"Cheaper prices\",\"They know where their food comes from\",\"Faster service\",\"Bigger portions\"]','They know where their food comes from',NULL,NULL,1,15),(239,8,'What is the main topic of this passage?','multiple_choice','[\"Sports\",\"The benefits of online learning\",\"Cooking\",\"Travel\"]','The benefits of online learning',NULL,'Online learning has transformed education in the 21st century. Students can now access courses from top universities around the world without leaving their homes. Platforms like Coursera, edX, and Khan Academy offer thousands of free and paid courses. Online learning provides flexibility, allowing students to study at their own pace. However, it also requires strong self-discipline and time management skills.',1,1),(240,8,'Name one platform mentioned for online learning.','multiple_choice','[\"Facebook\",\"Coursera\",\"Instagram\",\"YouTube\"]','Coursera',NULL,NULL,1,2),(241,8,'What skill does online learning require?','multiple_choice','[\"Cooking skills\",\"Self-discipline and time management\",\"Drawing skills\",\"Driving skills\"]','Self-discipline and time management',NULL,NULL,1,3),(242,8,'True or False: Online courses are only available for a fee.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','False',NULL,NULL,1,4),(243,8,'Fill in: Online learning provides _____ for students.','fill_blank',NULL,'flexibility',NULL,NULL,1,5),(244,8,'According to the passage, what do international students gain?','multiple_choice','[\"Only a degree\",\"Cultural understanding and global perspective\",\"Nothing special\",\"Just language skills\"]','Cultural understanding and global perspective',NULL,'Studying abroad is a dream for many students. Living in a foreign country helps students develop independence, learn a new language, and gain cultural understanding. Many universities offer exchange programs that last one or two semesters. While studying abroad can be expensive, there are many scholarships available. Students who study abroad often say it was the most valuable experience of their lives, giving them a global perspective and lifelong friendships.',1,6),(245,8,'How long do most exchange programs last?','multiple_choice','[\"One week\",\"One or two semesters\",\"Five years\",\"One day\"]','One or two semesters',NULL,NULL,1,7),(246,8,'What helps with the cost of studying abroad?','multiple_choice','[\"Nothing\",\"Scholarships\",\"Part-time jobs only\",\"Family loans only\"]','Scholarships',NULL,NULL,1,8),(247,8,'True or False: Students who study abroad often find it valuable.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','True',NULL,NULL,1,9),(248,8,'Fill in: Studying abroad helps develop _____.','fill_blank',NULL,'independence',NULL,NULL,1,10),(249,8,'What does STEM stand for in education?','multiple_choice','[\"Sports, Travel, English, Music\",\"Science, Technology, Engineering, Mathematics\",\"Study, Test, Exam, Mark\",\"School, Teacher, Education, Method\"]','Science, Technology, Engineering, Mathematics',NULL,'STEM education focuses on Science, Technology, Engineering, and Mathematics. Many countries are investing heavily in STEM programs because these fields are essential for innovation and economic growth. Schools are introducing coding and robotics classes from an early age. STEM careers are among the highest-paying and most in-demand jobs in the world. However, experts also emphasize the importance of combining STEM with arts and humanities for well-rounded education.',1,11),(250,8,'Why are countries investing in STEM?','multiple_choice','[\"For entertainment\",\"For innovation and economic growth\",\"For sports\",\"For tourism\"]','For innovation and economic growth',NULL,NULL,1,12),(251,8,'What new classes are schools introducing?','multiple_choice','[\"Cooking and sewing\",\"Coding and robotics\",\"Music and dance\",\"Drawing and painting\"]','Coding and robotics',NULL,NULL,1,13),(252,8,'True or False: STEM careers are generally low-paying.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','False',NULL,NULL,1,14),(253,8,'What should STEM be combined with for well-rounded education?','multiple_choice','[\"Sports only\",\"Arts and humanities\",\"Nothing\",\"More mathematics\"]','Arts and humanities',NULL,NULL,1,15),(254,10,'Listen: \"The password must be at least 8 characters.\" What is the minimum password length?','multiple_choice','[\"4 characters\",\"6 characters\",\"8 characters\",\"10 characters\"]','8 characters',NULL,NULL,1,1),(255,10,'Listen: \"Please restart your computer to apply the updates.\" What should you do?','multiple_choice','[\"Turn off the computer\",\"Restart the computer\",\"Delete the updates\",\"Ignore it\"]','Restart the computer',NULL,NULL,1,2),(256,10,'Listen: \"The file is too large to send by email.\" What is the problem?','multiple_choice','[\"Email is broken\",\"The file size is too big\",\"No internet\",\"Wrong address\"]','The file size is too big',NULL,NULL,1,3),(257,10,'Listen: \"You can store your files in the cloud.\" Where can files be stored?','multiple_choice','[\"In a drawer\",\"In the cloud\",\"On paper\",\"In a book\"]','In the cloud',NULL,NULL,1,4),(258,10,'Listen: \"Make sure to save your work before closing.\" What should you do first?','multiple_choice','[\"Close immediately\",\"Save your work\",\"Delete files\",\"Print everything\"]','Save your work',NULL,NULL,1,5),(259,10,'True or False: \"The website is down\" means the website is not working.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','True',NULL,NULL,1,6),(260,10,'Listen: \"She works as a software developer.\" What is her job?','multiple_choice','[\"Teacher\",\"Software developer\",\"Doctor\",\"Chef\"]','Software developer',NULL,NULL,1,7),(261,10,'Listen: \"The battery is running low. Please charge your laptop.\" What needs charging?','multiple_choice','[\"Phone\",\"Laptop\",\"Camera\",\"Tablet\"]','Laptop',NULL,NULL,1,8),(262,10,'Fill in: \"Please connect to the _____ network.\" (wireless internet)','fill_blank',NULL,'WiFi',NULL,NULL,1,9),(263,10,'Listen: \"Click on the download button to get the file.\" What button should you click?','multiple_choice','[\"Upload\",\"Delete\",\"Download\",\"Share\"]','Download',NULL,NULL,1,10),(264,10,'Listen: \"The printer is out of paper.\" What does the printer need?','multiple_choice','[\"Ink\",\"Paper\",\"Electricity\",\"WiFi\"]','Paper',NULL,NULL,1,11),(265,10,'True or False: \"Install the antivirus software\" means remove the protection.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','False',NULL,NULL,1,12),(266,10,'Listen: \"The meeting will be on Zoom at 3 PM.\" What platform is the meeting on?','multiple_choice','[\"Skype\",\"Teams\",\"Zoom\",\"Google Meet\"]','Zoom',NULL,NULL,1,13),(267,10,'Listen: \"He backed up all his photos to Google Drive.\" Where did he save his photos?','multiple_choice','[\"USB drive\",\"Google Drive\",\"CD\",\"Printed album\"]','Google Drive',NULL,NULL,1,14),(268,10,'Fill in: \"Do not click on suspicious _____ in emails.\" (web addresses)','fill_blank',NULL,'links',NULL,NULL,1,15),(269,12,'What is the main message of this passage?','multiple_choice','[\"Sleep is not important\",\"Getting enough sleep is crucial for health\",\"You should sleep less\",\"Sleep causes problems\"]','Getting enough sleep is crucial for health',NULL,'Sleep is one of the most important factors for good health. Adults need between 7 and 9 hours of sleep each night. Lack of sleep can lead to many health problems, including weakened immune system, weight gain, and poor concentration. To improve sleep quality, experts recommend maintaining a regular sleep schedule, avoiding screens before bedtime, and keeping the bedroom cool and dark. Good sleep hygiene can significantly improve both physical and mental health.',1,1),(270,12,'How many hours of sleep do adults need?','multiple_choice','[\"3-5 hours\",\"5-6 hours\",\"7-9 hours\",\"10-12 hours\"]','7-9 hours',NULL,NULL,1,2),(271,12,'What should you avoid before bedtime?','multiple_choice','[\"Reading\",\"Screens\",\"Drinking water\",\"Stretching\"]','Screens',NULL,NULL,1,3),(272,12,'True or False: Lack of sleep can weaken the immune system.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','True',NULL,NULL,1,4),(273,12,'Fill in: Good sleep _____ improves physical and mental health.','fill_blank',NULL,'hygiene',NULL,NULL,1,5),(274,12,'According to the passage, what reduces chronic disease risk?','multiple_choice','[\"Watching TV\",\"Regular exercise\",\"Playing video games\",\"Eating fast food\"]','Regular exercise',NULL,'Regular exercise is one of the best things you can do for your health. The World Health Organization recommends at least 150 minutes of moderate exercise per week. This can include walking, swimming, cycling, or dancing. Exercise helps control weight, reduces the risk of chronic diseases, improves mood, and boosts energy levels. Even small amounts of physical activity, like taking the stairs instead of the elevator, can make a significant difference in your overall health.',1,6),(275,12,'How many minutes of exercise per week does WHO recommend?','multiple_choice','[\"30 minutes\",\"60 minutes\",\"100 minutes\",\"150 minutes\"]','150 minutes',NULL,NULL,1,7),(276,12,'Which activities are mentioned as moderate exercise?','multiple_choice','[\"Sleeping and eating\",\"Walking, swimming, cycling, dancing\",\"Reading and writing\",\"Cooking and cleaning\"]','Walking, swimming, cycling, dancing',NULL,NULL,1,8),(277,12,'True or False: Only intense exercise is beneficial for health.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','False',NULL,NULL,1,9),(278,12,'Fill in: Taking the stairs instead of the _____ helps your health.','fill_blank',NULL,'elevator',NULL,NULL,1,10),(279,12,'What does the passage say about mental health?','multiple_choice','[\"It is not important\",\"It is just as important as physical health\",\"Only doctors need to worry about it\",\"It cannot be improved\"]','It is just as important as physical health',NULL,'Mental health is just as important as physical health. Stress, anxiety, and depression affect millions of people worldwide. There are many ways to improve mental health: regular exercise, meditation, spending time in nature, and talking to friends and family. It is important to recognize the signs of mental health problems and seek help when needed. Many workplaces now offer mental health support programs, and there is growing awareness about reducing the stigma around mental illness.',1,11),(280,12,'What are some common mental health issues mentioned?','multiple_choice','[\"Headache and fever\",\"Stress, anxiety, and depression\",\"Broken bones\",\"Allergies\"]','Stress, anxiety, and depression',NULL,NULL,1,12),(281,12,'How can you improve mental health?','multiple_choice','[\"Work more hours\",\"Exercise, meditation, nature, social connection\",\"Avoid all people\",\"Sleep all day\"]','Exercise, meditation, nature, social connection',NULL,NULL,1,13),(282,12,'True or False: There is growing awareness about mental health stigma.','true_false','[\"True\",\"False\"]','True',NULL,NULL,1,14),(283,12,'What do many workplaces now offer?','multiple_choice','[\"Free food\",\"Mental health support programs\",\"Gym memberships only\",\"Nothing\"]','Mental health support programs',NULL,NULL,1,15),(284,6,'What does \"assignment\" mean?','multiple_choice','[\"A type of test\", \"Homework or task given by a teacher\", \"A school building\", \"A textbook\"]','Homework or task given by a teacher',NULL,NULL,1,1),(285,6,'\"Scholarship\" refers to:','multiple_choice','[\"A type of school\", \"Financial aid for students\", \"A school uniform\", \"A sports team\"]','Financial aid for students',NULL,NULL,1,2),(286,6,'What is a \"semester\"?','multiple_choice','[\"A school subject\", \"Half of an academic year\", \"A graduation ceremony\", \"A type of exam\"]','Half of an academic year',NULL,NULL,1,3),(287,6,'What does \"graduate\" mean?','multiple_choice','[\"To start school\", \"To fail an exam\", \"To complete a degree program\", \"To skip a class\"]','To complete a degree program',NULL,NULL,1,4),(288,6,'\"Curriculum\" is:','multiple_choice','[\"A school building\", \"The subjects in a course of study\", \"A type of student\", \"A teacher\'s name\"]','The subjects in a course of study',NULL,NULL,1,5),(289,6,'What is a \"tutor\"?','multiple_choice','[\"A school bus driver\", \"A private teacher\", \"A school principal\", \"A janitor\"]','A private teacher',NULL,NULL,1,6),(290,6,'\"Enrollment\" means:','multiple_choice','[\"Graduation ceremony\", \"Dropping out of school\", \"Registering for school or classes\", \"A school holiday\"]','Registering for school or classes',NULL,NULL,1,7),(291,6,'A \"dormitory\" is:','multiple_choice','[\"A classroom\", \"A library\", \"A student residence building\", \"A cafeteria\"]','A student residence building',NULL,NULL,1,8),(292,6,'True or False: \"GPA\" stands for \"Grade Point Average\".','true_false','[\"True\", \"False\"]','True',NULL,NULL,1,9),(293,6,'Fill in the blank: The final _____ is next Monday.','fill_blank',NULL,'exam',NULL,NULL,1,10),(294,7,'What is \"software\"?','multiple_choice','[\"Physical parts of a computer\", \"Programs and applications\", \"A type of keyboard\", \"An internet cable\"]','Programs and applications',NULL,NULL,1,1),(295,7,'\"Hardware\" refers to:','multiple_choice','[\"Computer programs\", \"Physical components of a computer\", \"The internet\", \"A website\"]','Physical components of a computer',NULL,NULL,1,2),(296,7,'What is an \"algorithm\"?','multiple_choice','[\"A type of computer virus\", \"A step-by-step procedure for solving a problem\", \"A programming language\", \"A social media platform\"]','A step-by-step procedure for solving a problem',NULL,NULL,1,3),(297,7,'\"Cybersecurity\" is about:','multiple_choice','[\"Building robots\", \"Protecting computer systems from attacks\", \"Creating websites\", \"Selling computers\"]','Protecting computer systems from attacks',NULL,NULL,1,4),(298,7,'What does \"debugging\" mean?','multiple_choice','[\"Installing new software\", \"Finding and fixing errors in code\", \"Deleting files\", \"Downloading music\"]','Finding and fixing errors in code',NULL,NULL,1,5),(299,7,'\"Cloud computing\" means:','multiple_choice','[\"Computing during cloudy weather\", \"Using remote servers over the internet\", \"A type of laptop\", \"Using only offline software\"]','Using remote servers over the internet',NULL,NULL,1,6),(300,7,'What is \"encryption\"?','multiple_choice','[\"Making data faster\", \"Converting data into a coded form\", \"Deleting old files\", \"Printing documents\"]','Converting data into a coded form',NULL,NULL,1,7),(301,7,'\"Bandwidth\" refers to:','multiple_choice','[\"Screen size\", \"The speed and capacity of data transfer\", \"Computer weight\", \"Battery life\"]','The speed and capacity of data transfer',NULL,NULL,1,8),(302,7,'True or False: AI stands for \"Artificial Intelligence\".','true_false','[\"True\", \"False\"]','True',NULL,NULL,1,9),(303,7,'Fill in the blank: Chrome is the most popular web _____.','fill_blank',NULL,'browser',NULL,NULL,1,10),(304,8,'What is a \"symptom\"?','multiple_choice','[\"A type of medicine\", \"A sign of illness\", \"A doctor\'s name\", \"A hospital room\"]','A sign of illness',NULL,NULL,1,1),(305,8,'\"Prescription\" means:','multiple_choice','[\"A type of exercise\", \"A written order for medicine\", \"A healthy food\", \"A gym membership\"]','A written order for medicine',NULL,NULL,1,2),(306,8,'What does \"allergy\" mean?','multiple_choice','[\"A type of exercise\", \"A bad reaction to certain substances\", \"A vitamin supplement\", \"A meditation technique\"]','A bad reaction to certain substances',NULL,NULL,1,3),(307,8,'\"Nutrition\" refers to:','multiple_choice','[\"Physical exercise\", \"The process of getting proper food\", \"A type of sport\", \"A sleeping pattern\"]','The process of getting proper food',NULL,NULL,1,4),(308,8,'What is a \"vaccine\"?','multiple_choice','[\"A type of vitamin\", \"A substance to prevent diseases\", \"An exercise machine\", \"A medical tool\"]','A substance to prevent diseases',NULL,NULL,1,5),(309,8,'\"Calories\" are:','multiple_choice','[\"Types of vitamins\", \"Units of energy in food\", \"Types of exercise\", \"Medical instruments\"]','Units of energy in food',NULL,NULL,1,6),(310,8,'\"Meditation\" helps with:','multiple_choice','[\"Building muscle\", \"Reducing stress and relaxation\", \"Running faster\", \"Cooking better\"]','Reducing stress and relaxation',NULL,NULL,1,7),(311,8,'What does \"diagnosis\" mean?','multiple_choice','[\"A type of treatment\", \"Identifying a disease or condition\", \"A prescription\", \"A medical bill\"]','Identifying a disease or condition',NULL,NULL,1,8),(312,8,'True or False: \"Protein\" is a nutrient that helps build muscle.','true_false','[\"True\", \"False\"]','True',NULL,NULL,1,9),(313,8,'Fill in the blank: Regular _____ keeps you fit and healthy.','fill_blank',NULL,'exercise',NULL,NULL,1,10),(314,9,'What did the customer order for the main course?','multiple_choice','[\"Grilled salmon\", \"Roast chicken\", \"Pasta with mushroom sauce\", \"Vegetable stir-fry\"]','Grilled salmon',NULL,NULL,1,1),(315,9,'How did the customer describe the dessert?','multiple_choice','[\"Too sweet\", \"Absolutely delicious\", \"Too cold\", \"Very spicy\"]','Absolutely delicious',NULL,NULL,1,2),(316,9,'What drink did the customer choose?','multiple_choice','[\"Coffee\", \"Orange juice\", \"Sparkling water\", \"Green tea\"]','Sparkling water',NULL,NULL,1,3),(317,9,'What was the customer allergic to?','multiple_choice','[\"Milk\", \"Nuts\", \"Shellfish\", \"Eggs\"]','Nuts',NULL,NULL,1,4),(318,9,'True or False: The customer asked for the bill at the end.','true_false','[\"True\", \"False\"]','True',NULL,NULL,1,5),(319,10,'What is the main advantage of cloud computing mentioned in the passage?','multiple_choice','[\"It is free\", \"Users can access data from anywhere\", \"It makes computers faster\", \"It replaces all other technology\"]','Users can access data from anywhere',NULL,'Cloud computing has revolutionized the way businesses and individuals store and access data. Instead of relying on local servers and personal hard drives, cloud computing allows users to store data on remote servers accessed via the internet. This means that files, applications, and services can be accessed from anywhere with an internet connection. Major providers like Amazon Web Services, Microsoft Azure, and Google Cloud offer scalable solutions that can grow with a company\'s needs. One of the biggest advantages is cost savings, as companies no longer need to invest heavily in physical infrastructure. However, concerns about data security and privacy remain important considerations for any organization considering cloud adoption.',2,1),(320,10,'Which companies are mentioned as major cloud providers?','multiple_choice','[\"Apple, Samsung, and Sony\", \"Amazon, Microsoft, and Google\", \"Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram\", \"Intel, AMD, and NVIDIA\"]','Amazon, Microsoft, and Google',NULL,'Cloud computing has revolutionized the way businesses and individuals store and access data. Instead of relying on local servers and personal hard drives, cloud computing allows users to store data on remote servers accessed via the internet. This means that files, applications, and services can be accessed from anywhere with an internet connection. Major providers like Amazon Web Services, Microsoft Azure, and Google Cloud offer scalable solutions that can grow with a company\'s needs. One of the biggest advantages is cost savings, as companies no longer need to invest heavily in physical infrastructure. However, concerns about data security and privacy remain important considerations for any organization considering cloud adoption.',2,2),(321,10,'What concern is mentioned about cloud computing?','multiple_choice','[\"It is too expensive\", \"Data security and privacy\", \"It is too slow\", \"It uses too much electricity\"]','Data security and privacy',NULL,'Cloud computing has revolutionized the way businesses and individuals store and access data. Instead of relying on local servers and personal hard drives, cloud computing allows users to store data on remote servers accessed via the internet. This means that files, applications, and services can be accessed from anywhere with an internet connection. Major providers like Amazon Web Services, Microsoft Azure, and Google Cloud offer scalable solutions that can grow with a company\'s needs. One of the biggest advantages is cost savings, as companies no longer need to invest heavily in physical infrastructure. However, concerns about data security and privacy remain important considerations for any organization considering cloud adoption.',2,3),(322,10,'Fill in the blank: Cloud computing allows users to store data on _____ servers.','fill_blank',NULL,'remote',NULL,'Cloud computing has revolutionized the way businesses and individuals store and access data. Instead of relying on local servers and personal hard drives, cloud computing allows users to store data on remote servers accessed via the internet.',2,4),(323,11,'How many hours of sleep do adults need according to the passage?','multiple_choice','[\"5-6 hours\", \"6-7 hours\", \"7-9 hours\", \"10-12 hours\"]','7-9 hours',NULL,'Getting enough sleep is crucial for maintaining good health. Most adults need between 7 to 9 hours of sleep per night. During sleep, your body repairs tissues, produces important hormones, and strengthens the immune system. Lack of sleep can lead to serious health problems including obesity, heart disease, and depression. To improve your sleep quality, experts recommend maintaining a consistent sleep schedule, creating a comfortable sleep environment, avoiding caffeine and screens before bedtime, and getting regular exercise during the day. Remember, good sleep is not a luxury???it is a necessity for both physical and mental well-being.',2,1),(324,11,'Which of the following is NOT mentioned as a result of poor sleep?','multiple_choice','[\"Obesity\", \"Heart disease\", \"Better memory\", \"Depression\"]','Better memory',NULL,'Getting enough sleep is crucial for maintaining good health. Most adults need between 7 to 9 hours of sleep per night. During sleep, your body repairs tissues, produces important hormones, and strengthens the immune system. Lack of sleep can lead to serious health problems including obesity, heart disease, and depression. To improve your sleep quality, experts recommend maintaining a consistent sleep schedule, creating a comfortable sleep environment, avoiding caffeine and screens before bedtime, and getting regular exercise during the day. Remember, good sleep is not a luxury???it is a necessity for both physical and mental well-being.',2,2),(325,11,'What should you avoid before bedtime?','multiple_choice','[\"Water and fruit\", \"Caffeine and screens\", \"Reading books\", \"Listening to music\"]','Caffeine and screens',NULL,'Getting enough sleep is crucial for maintaining good health. Most adults need between 7 to 9 hours of sleep per night. During sleep, your body repairs tissues, produces important hormones, and strengthens the immune system. Lack of sleep can lead to serious health problems including obesity, heart disease, and depression. To improve your sleep quality, experts recommend maintaining a consistent sleep schedule, creating a comfortable sleep environment, avoiding caffeine and screens before bedtime, and getting regular exercise during the day. Remember, good sleep is not a luxury???it is a necessity for both physical and mental well-being.',2,3),(326,11,'True or False: The passage says good sleep is a necessity, not a luxury.','true_false','[\"True\", \"False\"]','True',NULL,'Getting enough sleep is crucial for maintaining good health. Remember, good sleep is not a luxury???it is a necessity for both physical and mental well-being.',2,4);
